+{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_019FNyL4GX1hERieTgkWvNk6","type":"tool_result","content":"     1→# Phase 5: Retry with Backoff\n     2→\n     3→Add automatic retry functionality so that failed tasks can be re-attempted with increasing delays.\n     4→\n     5→## Requirements\n     6→\n     7→- There should be a way to mark a processing task as completed or failed.\n     8→- When a task fails and has retries remaining, it is automatically re-added to the queue with a delay.\n     9→- The delay follows exponential backoff: `baseDelay * 2^(attempt - 1)` (e.g., 1s, 2s, 4s, ...).\n    10→- The default maximum number of retries is 3, but this should be configurable per task.\n    11→- The base backoff delay defaults to 1000ms but should be configurable per task.\n    12→- The task should track how many times it has been attempted.\n    13→- Retried tasks keep their original queue and priority.\n    14→- If all retries are exhausted, the task remains in a failed state.\n    15→"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"b7255fb0-57ab-4a91-9486-5bfa4e4e7cc3","uuid":"4630c89c-a46b-491f-a69c-648d9c8c6616","tool_use_result":{"type":"text","file":{"filePath":"/workspace/phases/phase-05.md","content":"# Phase 5: Retry with Backoff\n\nAdd automatic retry functionality so that failed tasks can be re-attempted with increasing delays.\n\n## Requirements\n\n- There should be a way to mark a processing task as completed or failed.\n- When a task fails and has retries remaining, it is automatically re-added to the queue with a delay.\n- The delay follows exponential backoff: `baseDelay * 2^(attempt - 1)` (e.g., 1s, 2s, 4s, ...).\n- The default maximum number of retries is 3, but this should be configurable per task.\n- The base backoff delay defaults to 1000ms but should be configurable per task.\n- The task should track how many times it has been attempted.\n- Retried tasks keep their original queue and priority.\n- If all retries are exhausted, the task remains in a failed state.\n","numLines":15,"startLine":1,"totalLines":15}}}
